123
00:06:31,093 --> 00:06:33,194
<i>Pojď dovnitř. Vejdi!

124
00:06:34,023 --> 00:06:35,124
<i>Vstup.

125
00:06:35,494 --> 00:06:36,533
<i>Pojď sem.

126
00:06:59,513 --> 00:07:00,754
O...omlouvám se.

127
00:07:10,533 --> 00:07:11,734
Hlupák.

128
